---
/**
 * Bhutan — "Where the earth touches the sky" intro.
 * Image left, content right (sticky scroll-friendly).
 */
---

<section id="bhutan-intro" class="bg-cream relative py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="container-edge mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

      {/* Image */}
      <div class="lg:col-span-6">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-sm shadow-[0_30px_60px_-30px_rgba(19,27,112,0.4)] img-zoom">
          <img src="/images/bhutan-hero.jpg" alt="Bhutan" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Copy */}
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:sticky lg:top-28">
        <p class="text-eyebrow text-brand-orange mb-6 reveal-fast">Bhutan</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h1 leading-[1.02] text-ink mb-8 reveal">
          Where the earth<br />
          touches the sky.
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-ink-soft text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p class="reveal">
            One of the world's last untouched countries, Bhutan is a place where
            tradition, tranquility and cultural integrity remain beautifully preserved.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal">
            Here, luxury is quiet — private audiences with monks, meditative walks
            along pine-scented trails, forest lodges steeped in calm, and riverside
            dinners beneath starlit skies.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal">
            This is more than a destination. It's a rare encounter with meaning.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal">
            For the discerning traveller, Bhutan offers an unparalleled blend of
            spiritual depth, vibrant culture, and breathtaking landscapes. Through
            thoughtfully curated Bhutan luxury tours, luxury is not defined by excess,
            but by the rare privilege of authenticity — private moments with monks,
            serene stays in valley-side lodges, and immersive encounters that nourish
            the soul.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
